hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: I'm interested in njie propud innehll I don’t know how you spent last weekend – but for many women up and down the country, it was devoted to filling jars with jams, chutneys and other glut-beating preserves. According to Homebase, sales of preserving jars, thermometers, jam funnels and gingham jam labels are up a pretty mind-blowing 2,000 per cent this year. (Which makes the gingham jam label-making industry not a bad one to be in. So yes, naturally I checked: Cath Kidston does indeed, savvily, offer a kit...)
